<rdf:Description
    rdf:about="http://www.notapathetic.com/comments/1158"
    trackback:ping="http://www.notapathetic.com/cgi-bin/trackback.cgi/1158"
    dc:title="Sack the lot and use Internet referenda..."
    dc:identifier="http://www.notapathetic.com/comments/1158"
    dc:description="Sack the lot and use Internet referenda.  We vote every 4-5 years based on a set of promises (which aren't always kept unless you have a PhD in semantics) and on the assumption that the people we elect will deal..."
    dc:creator="NotApathetic.com"
