	<p><em><strong>Gavin</strong> replies:</em> There are a massive number of holes in Labour's ID card plans. Check out The Register for some of the major issues. If they ever implement it, it'll be a massive waste of time and money and will, of course, make no difference to organised crime and torrorism, as Labour say it will.</p>
	<small>
